title: Time Travel: Princess, You Are So Sweet - Novel Updates
tags: Adapted to Manhua   Ancient Times   Beautiful Female Lead   Female Protagonist   Handsome Male Lead   Love Interest Falls in Love First   Time Travel   Transmigration
author: 郁紫紫
description:
It isn't difficult to face a situation like a sudden-pass-to-another-world because it has been a stereotype start for a fantastic journey. 

But waking up as the top girl at a brothel and finding herself trapped in the body of the General's daughter in another world is freaking unacceptable! 

Let alone there is an engagement with a playboy prince granted by the emperor waiting for her. 

What is it? A revenge? Or... Let's see how two haters fall for each other?

 'I like you it's my business,' said the prince.>
